HEADWORD: Tipstaff
<hw>Tip"staff`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Tipstaff</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A staff
tipped with metal.</def> <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An officer who bears a staff tipped with metal; a
